Latest Refresh Card 17

Step 1: Create Latest Refresh Card

- Choose the Card visual and insert LastRefresh under the Last Refreshed Date table into the field line.

- Select Format and under General X position = 950, Y position = 0, Width = 191, Height = 62

- Data Label = Font Color = black, text size = 11, font family = Constantia

- Category Label is off

- Title is on = Latest Refresh, Font color = black, text size = 11, font family = Constantia and alignment = centered

- Background is on = Color = light blue (same as all other blue)
